---
title: Spicy One-Pot Vegetarian Lentil Chili with Sour Cream, Cheddar, Scallions & Tortilla Chips
description: A loaded bowl of chili is one of life’s greatest pleasures, and this vegetarian version is no exception. Brimming with tomato, green pepper, and scallions, hearty lentils simmer in a spiced veggie broth until thick and flavorful. Load on the shredded cheddar, sour cream, and scallions, and serve with tortilla chips to scoop it all up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66df4bc148e223afaf60f419-d5167284.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66df4bc148e223afaf60f419-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spicy-one-pot-vegetarian-lentil-chili-66df4bc148e223afaf60f419
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
  fat: 24 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
  carbohydrates: 68 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 24 g
  fiber: 14 g
  sodium: 1770 mg
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
---

Wash and dry produce.

Trim and thinly slice @scallions{2%unit}, separating whites from greens. Core,
deseed, and finely dice @long green pepper{1%unit}. Dice @tomato{1%unit} into
1/2-inch pieces. Quarter @lime{1%unit}.

Heat a drizzle of @cooking oil{} in a #medium pot{} (large #pot{} for 4 servings)
over medium-high heat. Add scallion whites and green pepper; cook, stirring
occasionally, until browned and softened, ~{5-7%minutes}.

Stir in diced tomato, @tomato paste{1%unit}, and @savory paprika blend{1%tablespoon};
cook, stirring constantly, until combined and fragrant, ~{1%minute}.

Stir @lentils{1%unit} and their liquid, @Tex-Mex paste{1%unit}, @veggie stock
concentrate{1%unit}, and 1/2 cup water (1 cup for 4 servings) into pot with
veggies.

Bring to a simmer, then reduce heat to medium low. Cook, stirring frequently,
until flavors meld and chili has thickened slightly, ~{8-10%minutes}.

> TIP: If chili seems too thick, stir in water a splash at a time.

Divide chili between #bowls{}. Top with @sour cream{3%tablespoon},
@cheddar cheese{1/2%cup}(shredded), scallion greens, and a squeeze of
lime. Serve with @blue corn tortilla chips{1.5%ounce} and any remaining lime
wedges on the side.